      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TIPSY TESS (8) ran a scintillating 28.44 win over 498m at this track last start. In form and looks the one to beat again. I'M FREE (4) has a terrific record this track and trip with two wins and one placing from three starts. Comes off a (28.80) win last time, scoring by 6 lengths in a Grade 4/5 over 498m at this track. Looks suited here and can measure up. ASTON KINNIE (1) is a talented type and proved too strong last time to win by 1.3 lengths at this track in a handy 28.95 beating ASHY BEAR. Safe beginner who draws ideally on the inside. Can measure up again. GIDGEE BUG (2) recorded a 3.5 lengths win (28.79) in a Grade 4/5 last time at this track. Has already won two times from this draw.",
